{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a3d016b74d","title":"外交斗争必须高屋建领势如破竹","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"069c9bf711","index":0,"year":1958,"month":9,"day":19,"articleId":"a3d016b74d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji40","name":"毛泽东全集第40卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/40-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji40":{"comments":[{"id":"2749d243fe","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a3d016b74d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东关于对美斗争问题给周思来的复信。"},{"id":"89acb208c5","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a3d016b74d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指1958年9月18日夜周思来关于中美会谈和沿海军事斗争的策略问题给毛泽东的请示信。"},{"id":"4cd8291c5e","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a3d016b74d","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"王炳南（1908-1988），陕西奉天（今乾县）人，当时任中国驻波兰大使兼中美大使级会谈中方首席代表。叶飞（1914-1999），福建南安人，当时任中共福建省委书记、省长，福州军区政治委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"48aecf067a","type":"title","text":"外交斗争必须高屋建领势如破竹！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a3d016b74d"},{"id":"2749d243fe","type":"paragraph","text":"恩来同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a3d016b74d"},{"id":"89acb208c5","type":"paragraph","text":"十八日夜来信收到，极好，有了主动了，读完后很高兴，即照办。你来信及我这封复信，请即转发王炳南、叶飞飞二同志，使他们明白我们这种新方针、新策略，是主动的、攻势的和有理的高屋建领，势如破竹，是我们外交斗争的必须形态。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a3d016b74d"},{"id":"4cd8291c5e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a3d016b74d"},{"id":"af42b30e56","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十九日上午四时于合肥","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a3d016b74d"}],"page":{"id":"0f31d0a55b","publicationId":"maoquanji40","articleId":"a3d016b74d","start":239,"